  5,14,"And from those who said: \"We are Christians.\" We took their promise/covenant, so they forgot a luck (share) from what they were reminded with it, so We urged/excited to stir up between them the animosity and the intense hatred to the Resurrection Day, and God will inform them with what they were performing/producing"
  5,15,"You The Book`s people, Our messenger had come to you, he clarifies/shows to you much from what you were hiding from The Book, and He forgives/pardons from much, a light and clear/evident Book had come to you69from God"
  5,16,"God guides with it who followed His satisfaction, the security`s/peace`s ways/paths, and He brings them out from the darknesses to the light with His permission, and He guides them to a straight/direct road/way"
  5,17,"Those who said: \"That God, He is the Messiah Mary`s son.\" had disbelieved, say: \"So who owns/possesses from God a thing, if He wanted that He destroys the Messiah, Mary`s son, and his mother, and who (is) in the earth/Planet Earth all together? And to God (are) the skies/space and what (is) between them (B)`s ownership/kingdom , He creates what He wills/wants, and God (is) on every thing capable"